s (demo mode)\n\n=================== afj-cardiff-vault (11).html ===================\nSize: 121.7 KB\nTitle: AFJ Cardiff �?\" Secure Document Vault\nH1: AFJ Cardiff\nHeadings:\n  - Vault Settings\n  - AFJ Cardiff\n  - Document Inbox\n  - Review &amp; Digital Signature\n  - ${isArchive ? 'Audit Proof: Document Archive' : 'Document Secured &amp; Sealed'}\n  - AFJ Cardiff Secure Portal\nShop/merch hits:\n  L64:   <!-- Production: Oracle CDN. If unreachable: vault falls back to vanilla render() silently -->\n  L633: <p>The Data Controller shall process personal data only for the lawful purpose of media production,\n  L663:         'Database Actions \u001a SQL Workshop \u001a SQL Commands',\n  L1212:           &nbsp;LXD Container Hardening &mdash; Production Security &#9662;\n  L1288: ffmpeg -i workshop-raw.mp4 \\<br>\n\n=================== afj-cardiff-vault-hardened.html ===================\nSize: 6.6 KB\nTitle: AFJ Cardiff Vault �?\" Hardened Runtime\nHeadings:\n  - AFJ Cardiff Vault �?\" Hardened Runtime Build\n  - Booting Vault Runtime�?�\n  - �s� Vault Runtime Failure\n  - Data Processing Agreement\n  - Vault Runtime Online\n  - Organisation\n  - Legal Content\nShop/merch hits:\n  L197: Production: ${env.isProd}\n  L239:     // SW registration only in production\n\n=================== afj_scrollytelling.html ===================\nSize: 554.8 KB\nTitle: AFJ Cardiff | Scrollytelling Azonto Experience\nH1: Impact ThroughDance & Culture\nHeadings:\n  - Impact ThroughDance & Culture\n  - The Signal\n  - The Grounding\n  - The Dialogue\n  - Join the Movement\n  - Glossary of Terms\nShop/merch hits:\n  L562:             <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAA84AAAPgCAYAAADjsyUeAAEAAElEQVR4nOy9B5gkV3mv/1V1mLBa5SwhhBIIISQkE5SzBCKK\n  L581:             <img class=\"hero-logo\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAA84AAAPgCAYAAADjsyUeAAEAAElEQVR4nOy9B5gkV3mv/1V1mLBa5S\n  L663:             <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgA