uld be chat/forum related.\n\nLet me look at the actual content of:\n- June 25 11_53AM\n- June 20 8_50PM (1) COMMUNITY SUMMIT\n- June 20 8_50PM (2)\n- June 20 8_50PM FG Companion\n\nBut these are all small (under 1.5KB). They probably aren't full merch pages.\n\nHmm. The user is sure it's in \"Generated File\". Maybe:\n1. The merch page IS in one of these but I missed it because it's small\n2. Or maybe one of the Nostalgia D'Italia portals has a \"merch\" page hidden inside its content (since it's about a food shop/storefront, it might have merch examples)\n3. Or the merch page was generated more recently than what's in Downloads\n\nLet me search EVERY Generated File for the words \"merch\" and \"cardiff\" together to see if any have merch content AND are AFJ Cardiff.\n\nWait — let me check ALL files for \"AFJ Cardiff\" + product/merch signals. The user's premise is the merch page is in a Generated File. Let me see if any of these contain \"AFJ Cardiff\" with product/pricing/shipping patterns.",
